{"tid":855592,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"耶莫蘭高撩講波佬打交「希望他不會笠水」","createTime":"2018-10-10T06:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-23T05:03:54.000Z","uid":77606,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"849cfb530ab4755acd14b237f60fd73e8bd53f99","tid":855592,"uid":77606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:47:54.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=vnaf3LLGtUYd2jTxRifVD9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=62c0e6be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】韋斯咸前鋒耶莫蘭高被烏克蘭講波佬批評狀態不濟，生氣得欲跟對方講手不講口。<br />\n韋斯咸開季連輸4場後，重拾表現，耶莫蘭高（Andriy Yarmolenko）在擊敗愛華頓和曼聯時也有進賬，帶領球隊回升至第15位，但仍被國內輿論批評得體無完膚。 「年輕時，我經常跟別人打架，有贏有輸，但作為一個正常男人，打架是平常事。」韋斯咸不敵白禮頓，耶莫蘭高在剩下20分鐘時被換出，遂被烏克蘭講波佬高比哥夫（Wladimir Kobelkov）狠批。 於是，<span style=\"color: red;\">耶莫蘭高有意約戰那位講波佬，在擂台上解決紛爭，「我現在下戰書，下場就跟高比哥夫決一高下，也不想再聽到他的說話，報仇雪恥，我正在等待他的答覆。」</span> 烏克蘭將於周三友誼賽面對意大利，耶莫蘭高有份入選，相信亦會在歐洲國家聯賽對捷克時披甲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://更多now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E6%9B%B4%E5%A4%9Anow.com&d=vnaf3LLGtUYd2jTxRifVD9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=3bd50e10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">更多now.com</a>體育新聞及英超、西甲精華，請按此"},{"pid":"7258834b7de3113a6aadf27cadb25eaf5aec07f2","tid":855592,"uid":60658,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:48:48.000Z","msg":"G.Honeyman<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a21d97eddc17e650f07dd76ef87f5520ec2622f","tid":855592,"uid":19126,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:49:44.000Z","msg":"人地話你對腳廢你就同人講手，呢條友究竟係咪智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f13f119277a0d65068e7ec10128964eab78c12f","tid":855592,"uid":61271,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T06:50:49.000Z","msg":"威脅你生命既野獸<img src=